            <a href="#provision" style="font-size:14px;color:#52617A;text-decoration:none;padding:6px 0 6px 16px;margin-left:-1px;border-left:1px solid transparent" data-hover="color:#1772A8;border-left-color:#1772A8">Sign-in &amp; provisioning</a>
            <a href="#done" style="font-size:14px;color:#52617A;text-decoration:none;padding:6px 0 6px 16px;margin-left:-1px;border-left:1px solid transparent" data-hover="color:#1772A8;border-left-color:#1772A8">You're all set</a>
